encode/{typescript,python,shell}/*`.\n37: \n38: ## 3. TEST EXECUTION\n39: \n40: ### Preconditions\n41: \n42: 1. Target file exists at the specified path (or any equivalent `.json` under `.opencode/`).\n43: 2. Config sub-language reference set intact: 3 files under `references/opencode/config/`.\n44: \n45: ### Exact Command Sequence\n46: \n47: 1. Invoke sk-code with the prompt.\n48: 2. Capture loaded refs to `/tmp/skc-LS004-loaded-refs.txt`.\n49: 3. Verify: 3 config/* + 2 shared/* refs loaded; 0 other-sub-language refs.\n50: \n51: ### Pass/Fail Criteria\n52: \n53: - **PASS** iff: 3 config/* refs + 2 shared/* refs loaded AND 0 other-sub-language refs.\n54: - **FAIL** iff: any typescript/python/shell ref leaks.\n55: \n56: ### Failure Triage\n57: \n58: 1. Verify `.json` and `.jsonc` are mapped to CONFIG in SKILL.md sub-detection table.\n59: 2. Verify the package descriptor / graph-metadata files are not accidentally classified as typescript by an over-broad TS marker.\n60: \n61: ## 4. SOURCE FILES\n62: \n63: - `.opencode/skills/sk-code/SKILL.md` (sub-detection table).\n64: - `.opencode/skills/sk-code/references/opencode/config/{style_guide,quality_standards,quick_reference}.md`.\n65: \n66: ## 5. SOURCE METADATA\n67: \n68: - **Created**: 2026-05-04\n69: - **Critical path**: No\n70: - **Destructive**: No\n71: - **Concurrent-safe**: Yes\n72: - **Last validated**: pending first manual run\n\n(End of file - total 72 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"---\ntitle: \"LS-004: OPENCODE JSON/JSONC Sub-Detection\"\ndescription: \"Verify that within OPENCODE surface, JSON/JSONC extensions trigger loading of config/* references.\"\n---\n\n# LS-004: OPENCODE JSON/JSONC Sub-Detection\n\n## 1. OVERVIEW\n\nVerify language sub-detection for `.json` / `.jsonc` files within OPENCODE. Config ref set loads; other sub-language sets do not.\n\n## 2. SCENARIO CONTRACT\n\n**Realistic user request**: Add a derived metadata field to a packet's graph-metadata.json.\n\n**Exact prompt**:\n```\